00:11:32,040 --> 00:11:34,080
This is Midwest Center, do you copy?

306
00:11:34,200 --> 00:11:37,520
Global 1025.
Midwest Center, do you copy?

307
00:11:38,720 --> 00:11:40,480
P.D.O. 342.

