God, no.

327
00:13:04,080 --> 00:13:07,000
God, no.

328
00:13:07,960 --> 00:13:09,000
No!

329
00:13:10,440 --> 00:13:11,960
God, no.

330
00:13:12,400 --> 00:13:15,160
Get a large building or factory
