00:13:31,080 --> 00:13:32,320
She was at a conference in New York.

339
00:13:32,400 --> 00:13:34,680
- She'll meet us in Chicago.
- Does she know this is my case?

340
00:13:34,760 --> 00:13:38,040
She does now.
