366
00:15:48,400 --> 00:15:49,960
How many bodies
have we recovered so far?

367
00:15:50,040 --> 00:15:51,080
We got seventy.

368
00:15:51,160 --> 00:15:52,760
Let's start documenting the wreckage.

369
00:15:52,840 --> 00:15:56,720
Find the tail section wherever
the hell that is. Get the black box.

370
00:15:56,800 --> 00:15:57,800
Guess we'll start over here...

371
00:15:57,920 --> 00:16:00,000
- with the cockpit first.
- Mr. Dantley.

372
00:16:00,080 --> 00:16:01,320
- Yeah?
- I'm Stephen Royer.

373
00:16:01,400 --> 00:16:02,440
F.A.A. Regional Director.

374
00:16:02,520 --> 00:16:03,680
- Hello.
- Look I know... Hi.

375
00:16:03,760 --> 00:16:06,160
I know you people at N.T.S.B.
don't like to speculate.

376
00:16:06,240 --> 00:16:08,040
But it's been six hours
since this crash occurred.

377
00:16:08,120 --> 00:16:09,600
- Nobody's talked to the press.
- We don't speculate.

378
00:16:09,680 --> 00:16:12,880
Look, we got rumors on the Internet.
The Mayor has publicly condemned...

379
00:16:12,960 --> 00:16:14,800
- the air traffic control system.
- We don't speculate.

380
00:16:14,880 --> 00:16:16,720
I'm not asking you to do that.
But two planes...

381
00:16:16,800 --> 00:16:18,920
flying into each other is
not supposed to happen.

382
00:16:19,000 --> 00:16:20,120
Now, there are a lot of people
out there...

383
00:16:20,200 --> 00:16:21,520
that are very nervous. I just need...

384
00:16:21,600 --> 00:16:23,480
- some reassurance from your...
