A hundred and eighty-two on Global.
Three on P.D.O.

395
00:16:44,040 --> 00:16:48,080
When you're ready,
we can check out the cockpit.

396
00:16:48,560 --> 00:16:50,280
John, you alright?

397
00:16:50,680 --> 00:16:52,400
Is something wrong?

398
00:16:54,480 --> 00:16:57,880
- Catherine was on this flight.
