400
00:17:05,920 --> 00:17:07,320
I've no comment.

401
00:17:07,400 --> 00:17:09,760
I'm meeting
my chief investigator now.

402
00:17:09,840 --> 00:17:12,600
I'll be happy to answer
questions later.

403
00:17:12,680 --> 00:17:14,880
We haven't interviewed
the controller at Midwest yet.

404
00:17:14,960 --> 00:17:16,800
But we're looking into
the possibility that there may...

405
00:17:16,880 --> 00:17:19,280
have been a mis-communication
between him and the pilot.

406
00:17:19,360 --> 00:17:21,680
It's up to you, if you
want to release that to the press.

407
00:17:21,760 --> 00:17:23,720
Right now our priority is
the recovery of...

408
00:17:23,800 --> 00:17:26,520
- the bodies of the victims.
- Do we expect any survivors?

