00:18:15,480 --> 00:18:16,800
- will you?
- The appearance, John.

435
00:18:16,880 --> 00:18:18,920
Okay. Look, you can stay on.

436
00:18:19,000 --> 00:18:22,440
But if it becomes a conflict,
