437
00:18:22,520 --> 00:18:23,880
I want you to recuse yourself.

438
00:18:23,960 --> 00:18:25,160
- I will.
- Now, I'm gonna trust you on this.

439
00:18:25,240 --> 00:18:29,040
It won't be a conflict, sir.
